<div class="beer-background">
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row">
      <h1 class="col-md-12 text-center header pt-2 pb-2"><i class="fas fa-beer pr-4"></i>Lager Head<i class="fas fa-beer pl-4"></i></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-8 offset-2">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row mb-5">
            <div class="col-md-12 pl-0 pr-0">
              <div class="border pl-3 pr-3 pt-3 pb-3 desc mt-5">
                <p><strong>Welcome to LagerHead! By using our application, you will be able to enhance your experience at your favorite local brewery by learning more about the beers they offer and if they allow you to order food to their tap room. If they do, you can match your favorite grub eats  with your favorite brew! Our multiple functionalities include being able to search for a brewery, beer, and beer type easily at the touch of your fingertips,take our survey to match you up with the perfect pour of liquid bliss based on your answers, or you can place your beer choice in our hands by choosing a random hoppy beverage!</strong></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <br>
            <div class="col-md-12 pl-0 pr-0 justify-content-center">
              <form class="card card-sm mt-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card-body row no-gutters align-items-center">
                  <div class="col-auto">
                    <i class="fas fa-search h5 pt-2 pr-3 text-body"></i>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col">
                    <input class="form-control form-control-md form-control-borderless" type="search" placeholder="Search by Brewery, Beer Name, or Beer Type">
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-auto">
                    <button class="btn btn-md btn-success ml-3" type="submit"><strong>Search</strong></button>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 pt-3 pr-0 pb-3 pl-0 pr-0">
              <a href="/survey"><button type="button" class="float-right mr-5 btn btn-lg btn-info" id="survey-btn"><strong>Take the Survey</strong></button></a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 mt-3 mb-3 pl-0 pr-0 border border-top-0 border-bottom-0 border-right-0">
              <button type="button" class="ml-5 btn btn-lg btn-info" id="random-search"><strong>BEER ME!</strong></button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

